<paragraph blockId="6.[136,1452,158,580]" box="[189,1170,338,364]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,345,338,364]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145">Illustrations:</emphasis>
— 
<bibRefCitation author="Cabrera, A. L." box="[373,593,338,364]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" pagination="133 - 140" refId="ref4465" refString="Cabrera, A. L. (1940) Cuatro compuestas nuevas de la America Austral. Darwiniana 4: 133 - 140." type="journal article" year="1940">Cabrera (1940: 134</bibRefCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[605,669,338,364]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[136,229,1991,2013]" captionTargetBox="[228,1358,190,1966]" captionTargetId="figure-21@2.[228,1358,190,1966]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Holotype of Critoniopsis bradeana (RB00541935). Image: JSTOR Plants." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5556299" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5556299/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="145">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
), 
<bibRefCitation author="Cabrera, A. L. &amp; Dematteis, M." box="[693,1063,338,364]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" pagination="65 - 268" refId="ref4489" refString="Cabrera, A. L. &amp; Dematteis, M. (2009) Vernonieae. In: Cabrera, A. L., Dematteis, M. &amp; Freire, S. E. (Vol. Orgs). Compositae VI. Ramella, L. &amp; Perret, P. (series eds.), Flora del Paraguay fasc. 39., Conservatoire et Jardin Botanique de la Ville de Geneve, Geneva, pp 65 - 268." type="book chapter" year="2009">Cabrera &amp; Dematteis (2009: 238</bibRefCitation>
, Fig. 91).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[136,1452,158,580]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,265,374,400]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145">Notes:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName authority="Robinson (1992 b: 172)" authorityName="Robinson" authorityPageNumber="172" authorityYear="1992" box="[294,739,374,400]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Mesanthophora" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[294,471,374,400]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="145">Mesanthophora</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Robinson, H." box="[479,739,374,400]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" pagination="169 - 172" refId="ref6447" refString="Robinson, H. (1992 b) Mesanthophora, a new genus of Vernonieae (Asteraceae) from Paraguay. Novon 2: 169 - 172. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 3391681" type="journal article" year="1992">Robinson (1992b: 172)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is a small genus in the subtribe 
<taxonomicName box="[1104,1314,374,400]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" rank="subTribe" subTribe="Mesantophorineae">Mesantophorineae</taxonomicName>
, comprising glabrous perennial herbs associated with limestone soils, with decurrent auriculate leaves and capitula emerging from the middle of internodes (
<bibRefCitation author="Robinson, H." box="[439,621,446,472]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" pagination="149 - 174" refId="ref6562" refString="Robinson, H. (2007) Vernonieae. In: Kadereit, J. &amp; Jeffrey, C. (eds.) The families and genera of vascular plants, vol. 8. Springer, Berlin, Heidelberg &amp; New York, pp. 149 - 174." type="book chapter" year="2007">Robinson 2007</bibRefCitation>
). Two species are currently known: 
<taxonomicName authority="Robinson (1992 b: 172)" authorityName="Robinson" authorityPageNumber="172" authorityYear="1992" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Mesanthophora" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="brunneri">
<emphasis box="[1047,1333,446,472]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="145">Mesanthophora brunneri</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Robinson, H." pageId="6" pageNumber="145" pagination="169 - 172" refId="ref6447" refString="Robinson, H. (1992 b) Mesanthophora, a new genus of Vernonieae (Asteraceae) from Paraguay. Novon 2: 169 - 172. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 3391681" type="journal article" year="1992">Robinson (1992b: 172)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Robinson" authorityYear="1999" baseAuthorityName="Cabrera" baseAuthorityYear="1940" box="[337,446,483,508]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Mesanthophora" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rojasii">
<emphasis box="[337,446,483,508]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="145">M. rojasii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Cabrera, A. L. &amp; Dematteis, M." box="[461,767,482,508]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" pagination="65 - 268" refId="ref4489" refString="Cabrera, A. L. &amp; Dematteis, M. (2009) Vernonieae. In: Cabrera, A. L., Dematteis, M. &amp; Freire, S. E. (Vol. Orgs). Compositae VI. Ramella, L. &amp; Perret, P. (series eds.), Flora del Paraguay fasc. 39., Conservatoire et Jardin Botanique de la Ville de Geneve, Geneva, pp 65 - 268." type="book chapter" year="2009">Cabrera &amp; Dematteis 2009</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Hind, D. J. N." box="[779,902,482,508]" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" refId="ref5075" refString="Hind, D. J. N. (2011) An annotated preliminary checklist of the Compositae of Bolivia. Version 2." type="book" year="2011">Hind 2011</bibRefCitation>
). The former species is easily distinguished from the latter by its leaf shape (oblong-ovate vs. lanceolate) and leaf size (2–7 × 1–3 vs. 6–10 × 
<quantity box="[1177,1284,518,545]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.25" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="0.5" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" unit="cm" value="1.25" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="0.5">0.5–2 cm</quantity>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Dematteis, M. &amp; Salgado, C. R." pageId="6" pageNumber="145" pagination="69 - 75" refId="ref4692" refString="Dematteis, M. &amp; Salgado, C. R. (2001) Pollen morphology and chromosome number of Vernonia rojasii (Vernonieae, Asteraceae). Compositae Newsletter 36: 69 - 75." type="journal article" year="2001">Dematteis &amp; Salgado 2001</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5556307" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5556307" box="[136,1269,1538,1560]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5556307/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" startId="6.[136,229,1538,1560]" targetBox="[151,1431,609,1514]" targetPageId="6">
