Geographic distribution of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Robinson" authorityYear="1999" baseAuthorityName="Cabrera" baseAuthorityYear="1940" box="[520,740,1538,1560]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Mesanthophora" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="145" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rojasii">
